The undersigned is directed to say that with effect
from 8 th August, 1981l :-
(i) Shri Narayan Datt Tiwari, Minister of
Planning and Labour, relinquished the
office of Minister of Planning and assumed
the office of Minister of Industry. He
will continue to hold tem crary charge of
Ministry of Labour.
(ii) Shri Charanjit Chan an a, will continue to be
Minister of State in the Ministry of Indu stry.
(iii)Shri S.B.Chavan, Minister of Education and
Social Welfare, relinquished the office of
Minister of Education and Social Welfare and
assumed the office of Minister of Planning.
(iv) Smt.She ila Kaul, Minister of State in the
Ministries of Education and Social Velfare,
will look af ter the work of. the Ministries
of Education and Social Welfare temporarily.
